<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200802/934dc1eb05aa429d92a4f76ec5a6576b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这座城市</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">逐渐恢复着往日的活力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也有了更新的变化</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天，雨小荷通过11组图片</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">向大家展示一下疫情好转的济南的变化</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>树变绿楼变高</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一切都在成长</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">疫情，让整座城市都安静下来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最明显的就体现在城市的道路上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200802/bb58e9fb687c43a5a766bfc231ce2f19.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">疫情好转</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">道路上的车辆开始变多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一刻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才是这座城市该有的充满活力的样子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>推开窗敞开门</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>生意才能敞亮</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今年的春节</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和往年最大的不同</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是只能站在门外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等待从小窗口递出来的盒饭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200802/ff128e806dff4cddab0efabdcfa6cdc8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">疫情好转</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一夜之间门庭若市</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刚端上桌的烧烤瞬间就被洗劫一空</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">空气中弥漫着孜然和各种香料的味道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一刻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才是我们心心念念的烟火气儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>运动场的人们</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>仍是少年模样</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乍一眼看到空荡荡的篮球场</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还真是不太适应</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">运动场前的座椅都变得锈迹斑斑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200802/162fc739647346fc8bd5d20434c58ff7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">几个月之后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这里又出现了那一群抢篮板的男孩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一刻的他们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才是充满阳光的少年模样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>芙蓉街的老巷</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一个人的狂奔</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冷冷清清的芙蓉街</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">倒是有点一骑绝尘的感觉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">画面里那个奔跑的小女孩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">倒也成了这条老巷里唯一的风景</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200802/729c69d86b084703bffab5104032087c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">疫情过后的芙蓉街</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">慢慢恢复到昔日的拥挤和吵闹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">摩肩接踵的游客和冒着热气的小吃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一刻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才是济南人心中最热闹的老巷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>老年人广场舞</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>挡不住的热情</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小广场的长椅上孤零零坐着一位老人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">故意压低的帽檐儿和谨慎的口罩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将这位老人凝固在时光里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200802/da758f8bde66491f9cc315d66b5ce594.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">幸运的事情依旧发生在几个月之后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">跳广场舞的老奶奶又出现了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一刻的吵闹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们应该期盼已久了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>泉城路的激情</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>疫情无法阻挡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">疫情之下的恒隆广场</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仿佛一下子回到了十年前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还未营业的日子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">偶有一个路人经过只是匆匆一眼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200802/5aca478598b24a1a9e1b5a0bb91a1617.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">转眼半年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这里仿佛变成了另一个世界</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">络绎不绝的人群</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">漂亮精致的橱窗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有五彩缤纷的灯光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一刻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才是济南喧喧嚷嚷的激情所在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>寂静寒冷冬天</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>喧哗热闹夏夜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“时刻保持高度警惕、</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">随时做好应对准备”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冬日之时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样的横幅到处都有</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有那么一瞬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">感觉世界就是这般寂静了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200802/57c069d9a4454d9eba9dbd7ab3e7c5d7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">待到偶然一个夏夜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我看到广场上的人头攒动</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">听到远处的人声鼎沸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一刻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我知道热热闹闹的济南回来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>冷落了的泉广</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>喷泉都生气了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">上个冬天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">泉城广场的荷花音乐喷泉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">独自屹立在这里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">望着远处薄雾里的高楼和整座城市</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等待着济南的苏醒之日</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200802/cb938de7100941d199adf4687b4c59ca.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">百十个漫漫长夜之后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这座城市重新打开了快乐的开关</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人群、舞动，音乐、喷泉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有一路的灯光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在一瞬间活跃了起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一刻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才是泉城广场应有的模样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>最冷淡的景区</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>都在这个冬天</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">五龙潭景区的门口</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">张灯结彩的大红灯笼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">怎么也挡不住意外的萧条</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200802/d3563a1256f140c3a4a4448de2545269.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">半年后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">景区还是那个景区</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牌坊还是那块牌坊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唯一变化的就是时间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一刻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才是“恍若仙境”的五龙潭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>火车站</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一个城市的窗口</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这本是春运最紧锣密鼓的时分</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">火车站却变成了最特别的地方</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它照样输送着一位又一位旅客</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但它却无比“紧张”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200802/170a7ccd07ad41eba08d6ffb35b52760.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">火车站</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是一座城市的窗口</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人从这里进来也从这里出去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它将全国各地的人们带到这里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一刻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才是好客又包容的济南</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>夏天替代冬天</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>疫情将广场归还</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">上个冬天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无论走到哪里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都是穿着防护服</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在寒风中工作的医务人员</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200802/b5d6052dc38b44d8bc469d4b00ab4984.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">时至今日</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">临时搭建的检测棚逐渐撤销</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">家门口的广场又重新还给了调皮的孩子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一刻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">整个济南也“悦动”起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一系列图片</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将疫情好转前后的济南</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">展现得淋漓尽致</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如今，我们终于可以重新看到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">趵突泉喷涌的泉水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">泉城广场拥簇着喷泉的人群</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">芙蓉街宽厚里拥挤吵闹的人流</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以及马路上人来人往的车流</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200802/58c24d4236644cacb2d6b376da2ca31d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">济南的各大景区都已开放</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小吃街和夜市仍然是满满的烟火气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有空的时候不妨去看一看</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这热热闹闹的济南</p>
